  <refentry id="function.pg-fetch-all">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>pg_fetch_all</refname>
    <refpurpose>提取一行作为数组</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>说明</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>array</type><methodname>pg_fetch_all</methodname>
      <methodparam><type>resource</type><parameter>result</parameter></methodparam>
      <methodparam choice="opt"><type>int</type><parameter>row</parameter></methodparam>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
     <function>pg_fetch_all</function>
     从结果资源中返回一个包含有所有的行（元组/记录）的数组。如果没有更多行可供提取，则返回 &false;。
    </para>
    <para>
     参见 <function>pg_fetch_row</function>，<function>pg_fetch_array</function>，<function>pg_fetch_object</function> 和
    <function>pg_fetch_result</function>。
    </para>
    <para>
     <example>
      <title>PostgreSQL fetch array</title>
      <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php 
$conn = pg_pconnect ("dbname=publisher");
if (!$conn) {
    echo "An error occured.\n";
    exit;
}

$result = pg_query ($conn, "SELECT * FROM authors");
if (!$result) {
    echo "An error occured.\n";
    exit;
}

$arr = pg_fetch_all ($result, 0, PGSQL_NUM);

var_dump($arr);

?>
]]>
      </programlisting>
     </example>
    </para>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

